I love you too.

168
00:22:12,998 --> 00:22:15,466
Ponyo loves Sosuke!

169
00:22:56,208 --> 00:22:57,607
Ponyo!

170
00:22:59,044 --> 00:23:01,706
Ponyo!

171
00:23:06,218 --> 00:23:08,049
Ponyo!

172
00:23:09,955 --> 00:23:11,980
Sosuke!

173
00:23:13,158 --> 00:23:15,126
Ponyo!

174
00:24:16,731 --> 00:24:18,275
Listen, Sosuke.

175
00:24:18,295 --> 00:24:19,839
Maybe it was fate.

176
00:24:19,991 --> 00:24:22,221
It just can't be helped.

177
00:24:23,161 --> 00:24:25,129
Ponyo was born in the sea.

178
00:24:25,263 --> 00:24:27,288
She went back home, that's all.

179
00:24:27,899 --> 00:24:31,665
Anyway, let's hope that creepy guy is gone.

180
00:24:32,637 --> 00:24:33,661
One lick?

181
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:36,205
Hurry, it's melting!

182
00:24:39,644 --> 00:24:40,975
Not bad!

183
00:24:46,194 --> 00:24:47,807
Cheer up.

184
00:24:47,827 --> 00:24:49,440
Koichi will be home tonight.

185
00:24:50,555 --> 00:24:53,615
He'll be disappointed if you're feeling down.

186
00:25:19,885 --> 00:25:22,183
No more ocean today, okay?

187
00:25:49,414 --> 00:25:51,006
Sosuke?

188
00:25:51,917 --> 00:25:53,384
Time to come inside.

189
00:25:53,919 --> 00:25:58,379
Do you think this bucket will help Ponyo find us?

190
00:25:58,890 --> 00:26:01,882
There's only one way to find out.

191
00:26:16,051 --> 00:26:17,829
Can you get that, Sosuke?

192
00:26:17,849 --> 00:26:19,627
It must be Koichi.

193
00:26:21,980 --> 00:26:23,208
Hello?

194
00:26:23,348 --> 00:26:25,077
Yes, it's me.

195
00:26:25,850 --> 00:26:27,784
Yes, I'm fine.

196
00:26:27,929 --> 00:26:30,059
I can't get back tonight.

197
00:26:30,079 --> 00:26:32,209
I'll signal when I'm offshore.

198
00:26:32,534 --> 00:26:33,611
Okay.

199
00:26:33,631 --> 00:26:34,708
Here's Lisa.

200
00:26:36,304 --> 00:26:37,262
Koichi?

201
00:26:37,282 --> 00:26:38,240
Yes...

202
00:26:38,260 --> 00:26:39,218
What?!

203
00:26:39,998 --> 00:26:42,228
Can't you get out of it?

204
00:26:42,367 --> 00:26:46,133
Fine... leave your wife and son up on the cliff!

205
00:26:46,371 --> 00:26:47,929
I give up!

206
00:26:51,509 --> 00:26:52,806
Why bother?

207
00:26:53,378 --> 00:26:55,403
C'mon Sosuke, let's eat out!

208
00:26:56,581 --> 00:26:58,242
I want to eat here.

209
00:27:26,978 --> 00:27:28,036
There he is!

210
00:27:28,179 --> 00:27:30,943
Turn off the lights, Lisa.

211
00:27:54,949 --> 00:27:56,241
It's Sosuke!

212
00:27:56,261 --> 00:27:57,553
He's a genius.

213
00:27:57,573 --> 00:27:58,865
Only five years old.

214
00:27:59,010 --> 00:28:00,841
