I promised Ponyo I'd take care of her.

242
00:29:34,038 --> 00:29:36,608
I hope she isn't crying.

243
00:29:40,011 --> 00:29:43,538
Okay, let's cheer up!

244
00:29:44,382 --> 00:29:49,318
