273
00:31:35,937 --> 00:31:37,635
Look at me!

274
00:31:37,655 --> 00:31:39,353
Hands and feet!

275
00:31:40,565 --> 00:31:44,524
No... don't tell me you tasted human blood!

276
00:31:44,802 --> 00:31:46,133
Wanna see Sosuke!

277
00:31:46,281 --> 00:31:48,229
No!

278
00:31:48,249 --> 00:31:50,197
His blood has deranged your DNA!

279
00:31:50,375 --> 00:31:52,240
