282
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:07,980
I need more power.

283
00:32:21,472 --> 00:32:22,530
Let me out!

284
00:32:22,684 --> 00:32:25,782
Be still, you evil blood.

285
00:32:25,802 --> 00:32:28,900
Revert, revert!

286
00:32:38,256 --> 00:32:41,953
